data.oai_dc:dc: A nexus file having 49 concatenated mitochondrial DNA haplotypes (control region and cytochrome b gene) belong to the subgroup CAS-1 of the subspecies group Mus musculus castaneus (CAS) and a outgroup taxon belong to the subgroup CAS-2 (BRC3024). This nexus file was used to construct Neighbor-Net networks.
